<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Manager Promotion</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f9fafb; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">

    <table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"
           style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff;">
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; text-align: center; background-color: #1f2937; color: #ffffff;">
          <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">PDP Charts</h1>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: #111827; font-size: 20px;">
            Congratulations, <%= @user.name.presence || @user.email %>!
          </h2>

          <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; color: #374151;">
            You have just been promoted to <strong>Manager</strong> for
            <strong><%= @team.name %></strong>.
          </p>

          <% if @company %>
            <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; color: #374151;">
              Your team is part of <strong><%= @company.name %></strong>.
            </p>
          <% end %>

          <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; color: #374151;">
            As a manager, you can now oversee tasks, invite new team members, and track progress more effectively.
            We’re excited to see the impact you’ll make!
          </p>

          <div style="margin: 20px 0;">
            <a href="<%= root_url %>"
               style="text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 20px; background-color: #3b82f6;
                      color: #ffffff; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;">
              Visit Dashboard
            </a>
          </div>

          <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 20px 0;" />

          <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">
            If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email or contact your admin.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">
            &copy; <%= Time.now.year %> PDP Charts
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
